      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 22:42:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京将百威英博俄罗斯子公司的控制权移交给当地公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/putin-hands-control-of-inbev-efes-s-russian-unit-to-local-group</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京已将百威英博合资企业的控制权交给了一家当地公司，此举打乱了百威英博通过与土耳其合作伙伴达成协议退出俄罗斯的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/putin-hands-control-of-inbev-efes-s-russian-unit-to-local-group</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 15:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Adani Green 首席执行官 Singh 将卸任，在集团内担任新职务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/adani-green-ceo-amit-singh-to-step-down-take-new-role-in-group-m5b6brb3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该公司在周一的一份文件中表示，阿达尼绿色能源有限公司首席执行官阿米特·辛格将于 3 月 31 日辞去现任职务，并担任该集团国际能源业务的领导。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/adani-green-ceo-amit-singh-to-step-down-take-new-role-in-group-m5b6brb3</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Dec 2024 15:07:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度央行行长预期2025年经济增长前景更好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/india-banks-bad-loan-ratios-seen-worsening-by-2026-rbi-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度新任央行行长表示，在强劲的消费者和企业信心的推动下，印度经济明年可能出现反弹，这是他本月初上任以来首次公开发表有关增长前景的评论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-30/india-banks-bad-loan-ratios-seen-worsening-by-2026-rbi-says</guid>
